All Classes and Interfaces

Class
Description
ISudoku
Interface representing a simplified Sudoku helper service.
ISudokuAdapter
Adapter class that implements the ISudoku interface using a Sudoku instance.
Main
Main class to launch the Sudoku application using JavaFX.
Sudoku
Represents a Sudoku board and provides methods to initialize, solve, validate, and manipulate the game state.
Sudoku.Coordinate
Represents a coordinate (row, column) on the board.
SudokuController
Controller class for the Sudoku game interface.
SudokuStage
Custom JavaFX Stage for displaying the main Sudoku game interface.
